574
00:30:59,716 --> 00:31:02,597
who is already really good at that, really respected for that,

575
00:31:02,597 --> 00:31:05,978
in the hopes that that kind of thing can yield good results.

576
00:31:07,473 --> 00:31:11,036
Discipline lunches, we really like and try and encourage

577
00:31:11,036 --> 00:31:14,299
and push leads talking to other leads

578
00:31:14,299 --> 00:31:17,823
to learn about how things are going in their worlds.

579
00:31:17,823 --> 00:31:20,085
And it's a good place to kind of, again, build that 20%.

580
00:31:20,085 --> 00:31:24,229
And we also have these things called coaching labs,

581
00:31:24,229 --> 00:31:26,371
which I will talk about in more depth

582
00:31:26,371 --> 00:31:28,753
when we get to collaborative learning part.

583
00:31:30,322 --> 00:31:30,462
and a 10%.

