00:32:00,823 --> 00:32:03,184
So depending on whatever that thing is

594
00:32:03,184 --> 00:32:05,385
that we're trying to get somebody better at,

595
00:32:05,385 --> 00:32:08,826
we just pick and choose what might work and kind of build

596
00:32:08,826 --> 00:32:10,226
a plan for them from there.

597
00:32:12,172 --> 00:32:15,314
So what does this all look like in practice?

598
00:32:15,314 --> 00:32:17,176
Some more kind of practical examples

599
00:32:17,176 --> 00:32:20,979
so you know how we're trying to bring this to life.

600
00:32:20,979 --> 00:32:22,740
And we're going to look, again, because it's easy

601
00:32:22,740 --> 00:32:24,522
because I'm with the team, I'm going

602
00:32:24,522 --> 00:32:27,004
to tell you more about Overwatch,

603
00:32:27,004 --> 00:32:29,926
and particularly our art leadership team.

