00:32:47,753 --> 00:32:52,855
that good stuff. And that's how we're trying to fill that 70% bucket. 20% is, yes, we're

609
00:32:52,855 --> 00:33:00,419
utilizing one-on-ones as a mechanism to provide them support as they're in these new roles

610
00:33:00,419 --> 00:33:01,099
and

611
00:33:02,364 --> 00:33:04,785
falling down and failing and learning and picking them up

612
00:33:04,785 --> 00:33:06,446
and all that other good stuff.

