00:33:36,892 --> 00:33:42,655
and Seth Spalding, our really talented art manager, and dedicating some time to talk

623
00:33:42,655 --> 00:33:42,815
about

624
00:33:43,525 --> 00:33:46,668
for lack of a better term, the art of art direction.

